3.jpg"></p>
<p class=3D"paraNoIndent1">When trying to understand what a business should=
 be doing, we can draw a business activity model (see <a href=3D"https://le=
arning.oreilly.com/library/view/modelling-business-information/978178017353=
5/15_ch01.xhtml#fig1.4">Figure 1.4</a>). Both of these valuable techniques =
are derived from Peter Checkland=E2=80=99s Soft Systems Methodology.<sup><a=
 href=3D"https://learning.oreilly.com/library/view/modelling-business-infor=
mation/9781780173535/15_ch01.xhtml#ch00_5" id=3D"ch00-5" class=3D"totri-foo=
tnote">5</a></sup></p>
